  keywords  = {security of data;social networking (online);aggregated digital identity;blockchain technology;credits check;identity aggregation mechanism;online communities;online environment;online identity;online reputation information;personal digital reputations;personal online behavioral ratings;personal online digital identity;personal online ratings;smart contract management framework;smart contract management system;social dependency network;Companies;Facebook;Media;Privacy;Software;Blockchain;Digital Identity;Online Reputation;Smart Contract Utility},
